data.description: If you want "Move In Ready" look no further. This is a Beautiful Home with a great location in the desirable Arbor Ridge Subdivision. It features a wonderful floor plan, 3 Bedrooms/2 Baths along with a nice size master bedroom and bath. The master bath has double sinks, a garden tub, separate shower and plenty of storage space. A gourmet meal would not be a problem to master in this spacious kitchen with lots of cabinet space. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances and beautiful counter tops as a bonus to this home. Included in this floor plan is a spacious laundry room. If relaxing in the backyard is something you enjoy doing, this home is a must see for you because it has a large lot with a fenced backyard, covered patio and a storage shed along with a double carport. If you would like to have a personal tour of this home please look no further and give me a call
